THE JEWISH EXPERIENCE PROJECT 
Nathan L. Cohn, member of Temple Israel (formerly B'nai Abraham), discusses Springfield and the 1908 race riot, his family's furniture store, marriage, the Jewish community, and anti-Semitism.1 tape, 60 mins., 23 pp.
Interview by Syma Mendelsohn, 1973 
